<!-- About Me section -->
<section id="about" class="py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-8">About Me</h2>
        <p class="text-lg">
            I'm Emidblol, a passionate plane enthusiast with a special fondness for the Airbus A330. I'm also a dedicated SCP nerd, immersing myself in the intriguing world of the SCP Foundation.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg">
            Alongside my interests, I'm currently a student in secondary school, specializing in economics science. This academic pursuit allows me to explore the economic aspects of various industries, including aviation and gaming.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg">
            As a developer, I have a strong command of Svelte, Roblox, and JavaScript, enabling me to create exciting projects and contribute to the gaming community. In addition, I own and manage 416 Times, a newspaper where I share my insights and thoughts on various topics.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg">
            If you'd like to know more about my work, interests, or have any questions, feel free to reach out to me at <a href="mailto:contact@emidblol.dev" class="text-blue-300 hover:underline">contact@emidblol.dev</a>.
        </p>

        <!-- Add more content here -->
        <p class="text-lg">
            I have been captivated by aviation from a young age. The grace and power of airplanes, particularly the Airbus A330, have always fascinated me. Whether it's studying their aerodynamics, following aviation news, or even taking flight lessons, my passion for planes runs deep.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg">
            On the flip side, I'm an ardent fan of the SCP Foundation. The SCP universe is a collaborative writing project that explores the mysterious and supernatural through a collection of fictional documents. Being a part of the SCP community has allowed me to engage in creative storytelling and world-building.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg">
            Balancing my passions with my education has been an exciting journey. Currently, I'm pursuing a degree in economics science, where I delve into the intricacies of economic theory, market dynamics, and financial analysis. This academic background complements my interests, allowing me to analyze economic trends in the aviation and gaming industries.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>

